column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, (p.u-p.r) as #, (p.r-p.i) as #, (p.r-p.z) as #, (p.g-p.r) as #, p.type as obj_ph_type, p.petroRad_u, p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z, p.petroRadErr_u, p.petroRadErr_g, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroRadErr_i, p.petroRadErr_z, em.specobjid, em.bpt as obj_sp_type, em.z as redshift, #* (POWER (#, #) *POWER (dbo.fCosmoDl (em.z, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT) , #) )* (em.Flux_Hb_# * POWER (#, #) ) as lumin into mydb.dr1#_lcg from PhotoObj AS p, emissionLinesPort as em /*WHERE p.objid = em.specObjID AND em.EW_Hb_# > # AND #* (POWER (#, #) *POWER (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT) , #) )* (em.Flux_Hb_# * POWER (#, #) ) > (#* (#^#) ) */
